{
  "texts": [
    "The model of the human figure used in this context and shown in Fig. 1a has been downloaded.",
    "In this model, body parts were colored with the help of Blender, made more suitable for the course content, and transferred to the Spatial environment.",
    "Similarly, male and female figures were created in the Blender environment and transferred to the Spatial environment in accordance with the topics to be explained and to ensure integrity in the classroom environment.",
    "Figure 1b shows the colored human model, male and female figures in the classroom in a Spatial setting.",
    "Figure 1c shows the designs of various matching activities for the anatomy of the digestive system and nervous system."
  ]
}